187.
MOST IMMEDIATE
No.55/1/1/76-CF
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA(BHARAT SARKAR)
CAB INET SECRET ARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACH IVALAYA)
DEPLRTMENT OF CABINET AFFAIRS (MANTRIMANDAL KARYA VIBHAG)
New Delhi, 7 June, 1976.
17 Jyaistha, 1898(S).
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect
from forenoon of June 7, 1976, Shri Syed Mir Qasim assumed the
office of the Minister without Portfolio (Nirvibhag Mantri).
GP.Chathe
(G.P. Chadha)
for Cabinet Secretary,
To
All Membe
of the Council of Ministers.
Co py forwarded for information to the Deputy Chairman,
Planning Commission/All Members of the Planning Commission.
Co py forwarded for information to:-
Secretary to the Prime Minister(Pradh an Mantri ke Sachiv).
Joint Secretary to the Prime Minister(Pradh an Mantri ke
Sanyukt Sachiv),
Private Secretary to the Prime Minister( Pradhan Mantri ke
Niji Sachiv).
Co py forwarded to:-
Secretary to the President(Rashtrapati ke Sachiv).
Secretary to the Vice-President(Up-Rashtrapati, ke Sachiv).
GP. Chadhe
(G.P. Chadha)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Co py forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Govemment of India/Chairman,
Railway Board/Secretary, Election Commission/Secretary, Union
Public Service Commission/Comptroller and Auditor General of
India/Office of the Accountant General, Central Revenues
(Shri R.P. Sabharwal, hccounts Officer), for information.
*Ki.SHYAP*
350 copies.
2/-..

Co py forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of the
Govemment of India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha
Secretariat/Establishment Officer, Department of Personnel
and Administrative Reforms, for information.
GR. Chadha
(G.P. Chadha)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
*KASHYP*
350 copies.
